Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------ANIME-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候確實是殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個事實不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也就是我在這裡陳述這一切的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的認罪狀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿之後的兩週  誰都不記得他在班級裡存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有和他有著密切關係的我還記著他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得這只是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我趁著記憶還清晰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡記錄如何才能停止災難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  讓死者回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓死者回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是停止已經開始的災難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上小學的時候  有一個和她很像的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她指的是見崎同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎同學明明是獨生女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.41,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也沒和我同班過  大家都叫她「Misaki」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從見崎家的地址來看  應該不可能和你一個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  所以我才說奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左眼的眼罩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她四歲就失去了左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙參加這次的合宿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一個人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像殺了人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原  發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.09,0:04:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問你們倆一個問題  聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識風見智彥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在問你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見智彥這個人認識嗎  是個什麼樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然認識了  既是班長又是你的孽緣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了  出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎弄錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯？弄錯什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我徹底把他當成「另一個人」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…  該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是風見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下殺手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說謊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這種謊話有什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試探了他一下  因為他最近感覺很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  他竟然忘記了我們倆小時候一起幹過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學時候的事情也不太記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心去追問了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你其實不是風見吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你才是混入班級的另一個人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著他一下子就變得很緊張  慌了神  最後還對我發了火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑  果然是這傢伙沒錯  當時我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個磁帶所說的一樣  他死掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者回歸死亡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就都能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…殺了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是真的想殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個扭打在一起  到了外面的陽台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經倒在地上不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血從頭上流了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我變得害怕起來  跑到了走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到榊進了這間房間所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認了嗎  風見同學是不是「另一個人」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一個人」死掉的話  他馬上就會變成不存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們卻記得風見…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我弄錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  榊  到底怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯了  或者是還沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩樓的高度不一定會摔死人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡看不到樹叢的對面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在先確認風見同學是不是還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島同學  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你被人捅了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去偷看了一眼食堂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理員怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島同學  快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵什麼呢  恒一同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.18,0:08:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島同學  他受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人捅了一刀  而且食堂著大火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理員在裡面死了  被人殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那個犯人放的火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把前島同學抬到安全的地方  打119
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和多佳子的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  多佳子被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  你在哪兒  多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有見到杉浦同學和風見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到過風見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才他渾身是泥面無血色地來了我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說  敕使河原變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.80,0:10:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然氣勢洶洶地  問我發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我把磁帶的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒了  錄音機不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榊  風見呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前島同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他交給聽到慘叫跑出來的同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分頭找風見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有去每個房間讓大家逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這房子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且食堂已經是一片火海了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見也不知所蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂成一團了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點告訴三神老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  三神老師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道三神老師出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  現在先出去報警比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  得先確認三神老師是否安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和望月同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從下面傳過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  泉美也死了的話我也活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉美沒有我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者回歸死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敕使河原同學  快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說讓死者回歸死亡…  為什麼杉浦同學會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她聽了磁帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前的三班找到的吧  小椋告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來尋找停止災難的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  在這裡聽了磁帶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  從望月同學那兒拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為對策組成員一定得去聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  為什麼說見崎是死者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子從海邊回來以後  精神上受了很大打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把多佳子找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤澤同學  一個人太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對策組給三班同學的重要通知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要播放的磁帶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是十五年前  災難中途停止的那年遺留下來的磁帶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴大家如何才能停止災難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  讓死者回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓死者回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是停止已經開始的災難的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  十五年前的災難被中途阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且  今年的死者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以這麼說  是因為我在小學時和沒有失去左眼的見崎同學同校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在她卻失去了左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不完全地復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的見崎鳴是假冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.35,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死者回歸死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.80,0:16:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸死亡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死者…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三神老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以殺害自己的同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要讓死者回歸死亡  就不會再出現犧牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要殺了見崎就能阻止災難
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！這絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那死者到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我哥哥償命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意很滑  小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死者回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小椋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在走廊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從下面包抄他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得真的是見崎同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女的感覺很可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是…不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聞到什麼焦臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像說是火災來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我沒看見火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是食堂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡應該沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是食堂發生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒在食堂門口的前島同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是讓杉浦同學給…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是那個老太婆幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很礙事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你並不是死者  所以我不會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且泉美還蠻喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死者…回歸死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒一同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤澤同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳子！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎…鳴！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.53,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  赤澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦同學她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我不宰了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死者消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會發生這麼悲傷的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見崎！
